sayip-node-utils (1.0.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Announce only the default-route interface IPv4 for local IP by default.
  * Reject loopback addresses and stop skipping VPN interface prefixes.

 -- Jory A. Pratt, W5GLE <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Sun, 31 May 2026 14:00:00 -0600

sayip-node-utils (1.0.5-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Refactor core logic into /usr/lib/sayip-node-utils for testability.
  * Add /etc/default/sayip for playback timing, sound paths, and IP filtering.
  * Install sudoers rule so asterisk can halt/reboot via DTMF.
  * Derive playback waits from ulaw file size instead of fixed sleeps.
  * Validate IPs with IPAddr; skip virtual interfaces for local IP announce.
  * Require node number for halt/reboot unless --force is given.
  * Improve postinst/prerm/postrm lifecycle (reinstall updates, purge cleanup).
  * Add unit tests, RuboCop, and ShellCheck to CI.

 -- Jory A. Pratt, W5GLE <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Sun, 31 May 2026 12:00:00 -0600

